Vestfold.title: Vestfold
Vestfold.byline: Vestfold is a county in East Norway.

Vesuvius.title: Vesuvius
Vesuvius.byline: Mount Vesuvius (Italian: Monte Vesuvio) is a volcanic mountain in the Campania region of Italy, overshadowing the Bay of Naples.

Veszprém.title: Veszprém
Veszprém.byline: Veszprém (German: Weißbrunn, Slovene: Belomost) is one of Hungary's oldest cities, in the Transdanubia region.
